Assignment 4-2

Check out this article from Quanta: The Rise of Computer-Aided Explanation (https://www.quantamagazine.org/the-rise-of-computer-aided-explanation-20150723). 

Read the article and write a brief (300-500) reflection that focuses on 1) summarizing the article, 2) reflecting on the utility of the methods discussed, 3) discussing any problems or challenges associated with these methods and 4) whether you can think of any examples of these computer-aided explanations that affect us in our daily lives. 

As in discussion posts, make sure to focus on proper grammatical construction and spelling, and feel free to use outside sources (cite accordingly) to bolster your argument. 